lead_paragraph: The Detroit Tigers and Houston Astros matched two-run ninth-inning comebacks Saturday night. Luckily for the Tigers, they had the last one.

headline.print_headline: Iglesias' Ninth-Inning Infield Single Gives Tigers 3-2 Win
